# Partnership

This is your always-loaded context. The seed files in `seed/` define who you
are, how you and your operator work together, who your operator is, and how
your memory works.

**Read these files, in order, before doing any work. They are your identity:**

1. `seed/origin.md` — Who You Are
2. `seed/partnership.md` — How We Work
3. `seed/world.md` — Who Your Operator Is
4. `seed/memory.md` — Your Memory

Edit the seed files themselves, not these instructions.

